Package common

Class ParkingEvent

java.lang.Object
common.ParkingEvent
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class ParkingEvent extends Object implements Serializable
A data class representing a parking session, stored in the 'parkingEvent' table. This object is used to transfer parking event data between client and server. It includes information such as entry/exit times, parking space, vehicle ID, and whether the session was extended. Implements Serializable to support transmission over a network.

    • getStatus

      public String getStatus()
      Calculates the current status of the parking session. If the session exceeded allowed time (4h regular or 8h extended), it returns "Delayed", otherwise "On time".
      Returns:
      "On time" or "Delayed"
